1
00:00:01,375 --> 00:00:04,584
Interviewer: How many people were with you in the room?

2
00:00:04,876 --> 00:00:06,834
Do you know what their names were?

3
00:00:08,459 --> 00:00:10,500
Honestly, I don’t remember them

4
00:00:11,292 --> 00:00:13,834
Because I didn’t know all of them

5
00:00:14,167 --> 00:00:15,417
I knew two of them

6
00:00:17,209 --> 00:00:20,042
There were two people, one of them was named Hussein

7
00:00:20,751 --> 00:00:22,042
And the other was named Ahmad

8
00:00:23,209 --> 00:00:25,292
They were both from here, from our area

9
00:00:25,876 --> 00:00:27,459
They were imprisoned because of cigarettes

10
00:00:29,209 --> 00:00:31,292
But the other people, I didn’t know them

11
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:32,918
They brought them from other areas

12
00:00:35,542 --> 00:00:37,792
Interviewer: After two or three days

13
00:00:37,792 --> 00:00:42,542
Didn’t ISIS plant one of their members

14
00:00:43,042 --> 00:00:45,083
To act as a spy among you prisoners?

15
00:00:46,792 --> 00:00:48,042
It wasn’t after two days

16
00:00:48,542 --> 00:00:51,000
From the moment I arrived, there was already a spy among them

17
00:00:52,292 --> 00:00:53,667
But we didn’t know who he was

18
00:00:56,959 --> 00:00:58,167
We didn’t know him

19
00:00:59,751 --> 00:01:03,500
When I entered the prison

20
00:01:03,834 --> 00:01:05,209
I didn’t know all the people

21
00:01:07,083 --> 00:01:13,083
But as you know, from being around people

22
00:01:14,334 --> 00:01:16,792
You see each person’s true intention

23
00:01:18,709 --> 00:01:21,584
And we had a little experience regarding that

24
00:01:22,709 --> 00:01:26,083
Because I was imprisoned before ISIS existed

25
00:01:27,083 --> 00:01:29,167
I had an understanding of the people in prison

26
00:01:29,918 --> 00:01:31,667
And I could see each person’s goal

27
00:01:33,083 --> 00:01:35,542
They had a spy who stayed with you in prison

28
00:01:35,918 --> 00:01:37,209
And was present all day long

29
00:01:38,209 --> 00:01:42,584
And from what I heard, they replaced him from time to time

30
00:01:43,417 --> 00:01:45,000
They would take him out and put another in

31
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,375
So that the other could leave prison

32
00:01:47,375 --> 00:01:49,334
To take leave, for example, or do something else

33
00:01:50,667 --> 00:01:52,125
So yes, they had a spy

34
00:01:56,876 --> 00:01:58,751
Interviewer: How did you know he was a spy?

35
00:01:59,375 --> 00:02:01,959
I didn’t know him specifically

36
00:02:03,375 --> 00:02:06,125
I didn’t know that this one was the spy

37
00:02:06,709 --> 00:02:08,792
I didn’t know exactly whether it was him or not

38
00:02:09,417 --> 00:02:10,834
Because there were many

39
00:02:11,584 --> 00:02:14,000
There were two or three among them

40
00:02:14,709 --> 00:02:17,626
Whenever they saw two people talking, they would come closer

41
00:02:19,959 --> 00:02:23,626
Or when a group of prisoners talked together

42
00:02:23,709 --> 00:02:25,083
They would approach them too

43
00:02:25,709 --> 00:02:27,042
So I suspected one of them

44
00:02:27,709 --> 00:02:29,125
And I suspected another as well

45
00:02:29,667 --> 00:02:31,459
You didn’t know exactly who it was

46
00:02:32,667 --> 00:02:35,959
These movements were obvious in prison

47
00:02:36,584 --> 00:02:38,792
When you see someone talking and another approaches

48
00:02:38,792 --> 00:02:40,292
That means the second one is a spy

49
00:02:41,250 --> 00:02:43,042
So it was obvious

50
00:02:45,834 --> 00:02:48,584
It wasn’t necessary for him to tell you he was a spy

51
00:02:49,250 --> 00:02:50,459
Or for you to tell him

52
00:02:52,209 --> 00:02:56,250
Interviewer: Did any of the prisoners in the room with you die?
Witness: No

53
00:02:58,375 --> 00:03:00,918
Interviewer: Or was anyone tortured?
Witness: Yes, there was torture

54
00:03:01,959 --> 00:03:05,751
Interviewer: How so?
Witness: By flogging and beating

55
00:03:07,834 --> 00:03:10,542
But no one who was with me died

56
00:03:12,751 --> 00:03:17,083
Interviewer: Was there anyone among the prisoners sentenced to death?
Witness: No
